[normal]Written evidence from the[bold] [bold]London[bold] Borough of Enfield[bold] [bold](SLC 030)[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Executive [bold]Summary[bold]&#xa0;
